1
00:00:05,714 --> 00:00:08,410
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,483 --> 00:00:12,351
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,421 --> 00:00:16,414
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,758 --> 00:00:19,249
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,328 --> 00:00:23,389
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,465 --> 00:00:27,424
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,904 --> 00:00:33,637
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,343 --> 00:00:37,312
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,748 --> 00:00:41,841
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,584 --> 00:00:43,881
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,219 --> 00:00:46,779
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,830 --> 00:01:00,200
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,402 --> 00:01:01,562
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,637 --> 00:01:05,437
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,774 --> 00:01:10,973
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,246 --> 00:01:12,577
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,648 --> 00:01:14,047
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,116 --> 00:01:20,385
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:34,871 --> 00:01:36,964
Tenten vs. Temari

20
00:01:38,274 --> 00:01:39,468
The fifth battle...

21
00:01:40,210 --> 00:01:44,010
Tenten, Temari... come forward!

22
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:53,921
<i>Seeing that made me all fired up, too!</i>

23
00:01:55,525 --> 00:01:58,688
Now... The second one from
the Land of Sand, huh...

24
00:01:59,128 --> 00:02:00,095
Do your best!

25
00:02:00,163 --> 00:02:01,687
- Tenten!
- It looks like it's going to be interesting.

26
00:02:16,846 --> 00:02:17,505
Begin!

27
00:02:18,314 --> 00:02:24,219
Killer Kunoichi and a Shaky Shikamaru

28
00:02:30,493 --> 00:02:32,654
Go for it, Tenten!

29
00:02:32,729 --> 00:02:34,492
Believe in your own strength, Tenten!

30
00:02:34,964 --> 00:02:37,626
We're behind you, Tenten!

31
00:02:37,834 --> 00:02:40,098
Knock her with all your strength!

32
00:02:40,670 --> 00:02:41,329
That's good!

33
00:02:41,704 --> 00:02:44,264
Cheer her on more, more,
more with passion, Lee!

34
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:44,829
Yeah!

35
00:02:46,142 --> 00:02:48,133
These guys are noisy!

36
00:02:56,686 --> 00:02:59,678
That spacing is just what I'd expect
from Tenten,

37
00:03:00,156 --> 00:03:01,885
not too close, not too far.

38
00:03:02,458 --> 00:03:05,552
Attacks or defense,
she can respond to either one.

39
00:03:05,995 --> 00:03:06,757
What happened?

40
00:03:08,131 --> 00:03:09,098
Please begin.

41
00:03:12,201 --> 00:03:14,863
Are you planning to wait out and
see how I make my move?

42
00:03:15,171 --> 00:03:16,331
Let me just tell you,

43
00:03:16,406 --> 00:03:19,500
once I start my attack
you'll be over in a second.

44
00:03:21,978 --> 00:03:24,538
You're trying to be cool and
see what I do first...

45
00:03:25,048 --> 00:03:26,538
A hundred years too early!

46
00:03:27,550 --> 00:03:29,245
It doesn't matter to me, come first.

47
00:03:29,852 --> 00:03:31,183
You said it...

48
00:03:32,288 --> 00:03:33,949
Well, I won't hold back.

49
00:03:40,797 --> 00:03:41,661
They missed?

50
00:03:41,731 --> 00:03:42,891
That's impossible!

51
00:03:42,966 --> 00:03:45,264
What happened?
Is that a warm up?

52
00:03:45,868 --> 00:03:49,269
Or are you scared and your aim is off?

53
00:03:50,573 --> 00:03:52,905
I thought I would enjoy it
a little bit more,

54
00:03:53,409 --> 00:03:56,071
but evidently it's not promising.

55
00:03:57,714 --> 00:03:58,305
No way!

56
00:03:58,815 --> 00:04:00,749
I can't believe Tenten's attack missed!

57
00:04:01,417 --> 00:04:02,679
It's unbelievable indeed.

58
00:04:03,519 --> 00:04:04,884
Tenten's weapons...

59
00:04:06,055 --> 00:04:07,682
always hits the mark
ten out of ten times.

60
00:04:07,924 --> 00:04:09,255
There no reason for them to miss.

61
00:04:10,193 --> 00:04:13,651
That's right...
She didn't miss.

62
00:04:14,097 --> 00:04:15,257
She was made to miss.

63
00:04:16,933 --> 00:04:19,868
As always, she's being disagreeable.

64
00:04:20,503 --> 00:04:21,367
How foolish...

65
00:04:22,505 --> 00:04:24,063
How disgraceful!

66
00:04:24,841 --> 00:04:25,432
Huh?

67
00:04:26,142 --> 00:04:27,700
Sand wins again.

68
00:04:27,777 --> 00:04:30,075
We don't know that yet.

69
00:04:30,947 --> 00:04:31,936
We know.

70
00:04:32,448 --> 00:04:34,848
How?
How do we know?

71
00:04:35,685 --> 00:04:37,915
Explain it so I understand!

72
00:04:38,621 --> 00:04:42,182
Stupid... As if I'd do
such a bothersome thing.

73
00:04:43,926 --> 00:04:46,793
Shikamaru said it so,
surely that's how it is.

74
00:04:48,331 --> 00:04:51,789
These guys are hard to understand.

75
00:04:55,038 --> 00:04:56,027
<i>Calm down...</i>

76
00:04:57,073 --> 00:04:58,938
<i>Don't let her get to you...</i>

77
00:05:00,576 --> 00:05:01,133
<i>One.</i>

78
00:05:02,445 --> 00:05:03,036
<i>Two.</i>

79
00:05:04,580 --> 00:05:05,171
<i>Three...</i>

80
00:05:07,116 --> 00:05:08,515
<i>If it's gonna get dodged,</i>

81
00:05:08,885 --> 00:05:10,477
<i>I just have to make</i>
<i>it impossible to!</i>

82
00:05:12,989 --> 00:05:16,618
<i>So she's measuring the spacing,</i>
<i>next one is going to be the big attack.</i>

83
00:05:18,761 --> 00:05:19,455
<i>I get it...</i>

84
00:05:19,829 --> 00:05:21,421
<i>So, that fan is the secret.</i>

85
00:05:21,898 --> 00:05:22,557
<i>If so...</i>

86
00:05:32,375 --> 00:05:33,842
How about... this?!

87
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:55,192
No way!

88
00:05:55,731 --> 00:05:57,062
My flying weapons!

89
00:05:58,101 --> 00:05:59,932
<i>Is there a secret mechanism</i>
<i>in the fan?</i>

90
00:06:02,271 --> 00:06:03,033
This is...

91
00:06:03,306 --> 00:06:04,330
the first star.

92
00:06:04,907 --> 00:06:05,965
There are two more.

93
00:06:07,810 --> 00:06:09,641
When the third star appears,

94
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,879
you will lose.

95
00:06:16,052 --> 00:06:16,882
Tenten!

96
00:06:17,487 --> 00:06:20,888
Don't be taken in by
your opponent, be calm!

97
00:06:21,257 --> 00:06:22,781
Be calm!

98
00:06:24,227 --> 00:06:25,194
<i>I know...</i>

99
00:06:25,394 --> 00:06:28,295
<i>Lee, I really intended to use</i>
<i>this in the main battle,</i>

100
00:06:28,364 --> 00:06:30,025
<i>not the preliminary round</i>

101
00:06:30,900 --> 00:06:32,458
<i>but it looks like I can't do it that way.</i>

102
00:06:39,342 --> 00:06:41,207
She's already going to use it?

103
00:06:44,347 --> 00:06:46,042
Pulling out two scrolls?

104
00:06:46,516 --> 00:06:48,108
What does she intend to do?

105
00:06:54,924 --> 00:06:57,916
Hah! No matter what you do,
it won't work.

106
00:07:03,733 --> 00:07:05,200
Rising Twin Dragons!

107
00:07:26,522 --> 00:07:29,753
Even if you increase the amount,
it's still the same!

108
00:07:31,093 --> 00:07:31,923
Second star!

109
00:07:40,503 --> 00:07:41,595
I'm not done yet!

110
00:08:00,690 --> 00:08:01,384
<i>Did I do it?</i>

111
00:08:17,707 --> 00:08:19,038
Third star.

112
00:08:24,947 --> 00:08:25,641
<i>She disappeared!</i>

113
00:08:28,684 --> 00:08:29,378
Where is she?

114
00:08:31,487 --> 00:08:32,317
I'm over here!

115
00:08:33,055 --> 00:08:33,612
<i>Damn!</i>

116
00:08:50,473 --> 00:08:51,497
Ninja Art!

117
00:08:53,676 --> 00:08:54,574
Wind Scythe Jutsu!

118
00:08:57,647 --> 00:08:58,443
Tenten!

119
00:09:10,192 --> 00:09:12,683
Chakra is enfolded in that wind.

120
00:09:12,962 --> 00:09:13,451
Huh?!

121
00:09:14,163 --> 00:09:15,653
<i>Tenten fought well...</i>

122
00:09:16,666 --> 00:09:20,966
<i>But she won't be able to escape from</i>
<i>that twister.</i>

123
00:09:29,779 --> 00:09:31,974
T-That's awful.

124
00:09:33,049 --> 00:09:33,947
Tenten!

125
00:09:35,318 --> 00:09:38,446
How boring... really.

126
00:09:40,323 --> 00:09:43,417
To think she completely intercepted
Tenten's weapon attacks.

127
00:09:43,926 --> 00:09:45,154
This is ridiculous!

128
00:09:45,961 --> 00:09:48,122
What's going on with her?

129
00:09:48,898 --> 00:09:52,766
It's just like Shikamaru said,
it's the Sand's win.

130
00:09:53,536 --> 00:09:55,060
That's why I said it.

131
00:09:55,905 --> 00:09:58,999
There's no reason for us to lose here.

132
00:10:01,644 --> 00:10:05,080
The Land of Sand is to be feared...

133
00:10:07,717 --> 00:10:10,345
Temari wins the fifth battle.

134
00:10:12,621 --> 00:10:13,417
Oh no!

135
00:10:29,538 --> 00:10:30,596
Nice catch.

136
00:10:31,607 --> 00:10:32,835
What are you doing?!

137
00:10:33,442 --> 00:10:36,843
Is that something you do to
an opponent who fought to the utmost?!

138
00:10:38,180 --> 00:10:39,340
You're annoying!

139
00:10:39,648 --> 00:10:41,707
Take that trash away already!

140
00:10:42,785 --> 00:10:43,911
Stop! Lee!

141
00:10:44,286 --> 00:10:45,981
Leaf Hurricane!

142
00:10:47,490 --> 00:10:48,013
What?!

143
00:10:48,591 --> 00:10:49,819
You're just like you look...

144
00:10:50,259 --> 00:10:52,420
You're dull too.

145
00:10:52,661 --> 00:10:53,753
What did you say?!

146
00:10:54,964 --> 00:10:55,692
Stop! Lee!

147
00:10:56,866 --> 00:10:57,628
Guy Sensei!

148
00:10:59,368 --> 00:11:00,096
Temari.

149
00:11:00,970 --> 00:11:04,406
Come up quick, you've been
declared the winner.

150
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:09,773
Don't keep company with that awful-looking
guy and his chaperone forever.

151
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:11,577
What?!

152
00:11:21,223 --> 00:11:22,918
That's enough, Lee.

153
00:11:27,963 --> 00:11:28,930
Gentlemen of Sand...

154
00:11:29,965 --> 00:11:32,957
I wonder if I may give you
a word of warning.

155
00:11:35,471 --> 00:11:36,938
This kid is strong.

156
00:11:37,540 --> 00:11:39,303
You should prepare yourselves.

157
00:11:42,778 --> 00:11:45,269
Picking a fight with the Sand...

158
00:11:46,482 --> 00:11:49,974
I absolutely wouldn't want to
do it with those guys.

159
00:11:50,953 --> 00:11:53,080
T-They're all awesome guys...

160
00:11:59,061 --> 00:12:01,427
Don't lose to those guys!

161
00:12:01,664 --> 00:12:02,358
Naruto!

162
00:12:03,365 --> 00:12:04,195
S-Sakura.

163
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:07,569
Sakura... Are you okay already?

164
00:12:07,937 --> 00:12:11,270
Never mind that,
you should worry about yourself!

165
00:12:11,607 --> 00:12:15,600
Huh? Me? I don't have
an injury or anything.

166
00:12:15,811 --> 00:12:17,108
That's not what I mean.

167
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:20,278
If you lose here, it's a point of dishonor.

168
00:12:20,616 --> 00:12:22,345
You'd be ashamed to face Sasuke!

169
00:12:22,785 --> 00:12:24,150
Y-Yeah.

170
00:12:24,987 --> 00:12:25,612
And...

171
00:12:27,223 --> 00:12:28,281
Thanks for earlier...

172
00:12:29,191 --> 00:12:30,351
<i>No!</i>

173
00:12:31,093 --> 00:12:32,583
<i>Sakura!</i>

174
00:12:34,530 --> 00:12:36,623
<i>You did your hardest</i>
<i>to get here!</i>

175
00:12:36,799 --> 00:12:40,257
<i>You'll disgrace women if</i>
<i>you lose to that Sasuke obsessed girl!</i>

176
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:44,506
If it weren't for your stupid cheering
at that time...

177
00:12:45,708 --> 00:12:48,336
I would have been soundly
beaten by Ino.

178
00:12:49,044 --> 00:12:50,443
Yeah, that's right.

179
00:12:51,347 --> 00:12:52,245
Y-You!

180
00:12:56,685 --> 00:12:59,745
Okay, hurry hurry!
Me next!

181
00:12:59,822 --> 00:13:01,414
Next!
Next is my turn!

182
00:13:02,358 --> 00:13:04,223
Shikamaru Nara vs. Tsuchi Kin

183
00:13:04,727 --> 00:13:06,058
Damn!

184
00:13:07,096 --> 00:13:07,926
It's me.

185
00:13:08,697 --> 00:13:11,860
Shikamaru, don't lose!

186
00:13:12,201 --> 00:13:14,169
- Show us that you're a real man!
- All right, all right.

187
00:13:14,603 --> 00:13:17,037
Get her with the 16 combo, go!

188
00:13:17,740 --> 00:13:20,538
- Win Shikamaru!
- <i>Ino's become super energetic.</i>

189
00:13:20,743 --> 00:13:22,904
You go for it!

190
00:13:23,612 --> 00:13:25,580
That guy manipulates shadows.

191
00:13:26,081 --> 00:13:27,810
Be careful of the shadows...

192
00:13:30,386 --> 00:13:33,150
I won't be beaten by
a stupid technique like that.

193
00:13:36,707 --> 00:13:37,674
Shikamaru!

194
00:13:37,741 --> 00:13:40,642
Bash that one around!
And while you're at it...

195
00:13:40,711 --> 00:13:42,508
Man, what a pain.

196
00:13:43,113 --> 00:13:45,707
Furthermore, my opponent is a woman...
It's hard to get to it.

197
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:48,775
If that's what you think,
I'll end this quickly.

198
00:13:49,086 --> 00:13:50,576
Go, go! Shikamaru!

199
00:13:50,721 --> 00:13:54,521
<i>Well, you could say that</i>
<i>I know these guys' raw power</i>

200
00:13:54,591 --> 00:13:56,218
<i>from that incident from the second test...</i>

201
00:13:59,896 --> 00:14:02,990
<i>I don't know anything about this one's Jutsu.</i>

202
00:14:05,636 --> 00:14:08,799
<i>On top of that, she's seen my Jutsu...</i>

203
00:14:10,073 --> 00:14:12,268
- The sixth battle.
- <i>That being said, for me...</i>

204
00:14:12,643 --> 00:14:13,769
Shikamaru versus Kin!

205
00:14:15,245 --> 00:14:15,870
Begin!

206
00:14:16,647 --> 00:14:17,773
I can only do this.

207
00:14:18,582 --> 00:14:20,243
One trick pony, huh?

208
00:14:20,917 --> 00:14:21,542
Shut up!

209
00:14:22,953 --> 00:14:24,978
<i>Ninja Art, Shadow Possession Jutsu!</i>

210
00:14:25,622 --> 00:14:26,213
That Jutsu!

211
00:14:26,590 --> 00:14:30,117
It's nothing if I just pay attention
to the movement of your shadow!

212
00:14:37,534 --> 00:14:38,193
Bells?

213
00:14:39,836 --> 00:14:41,895
Heh, that's a classic.

214
00:14:42,839 --> 00:14:44,966
Next, you'll throw Senbons with bells

215
00:14:45,175 --> 00:14:47,769
and Senbons without bells
at the same time, right?

216
00:14:49,146 --> 00:14:52,843
I'll respond to the sound of the bells,
intending to dodge them.

217
00:14:54,084 --> 00:14:57,611
But I won't notice the quiet Senbons,
and, ouch.

218
00:14:58,922 --> 00:14:59,581
Is that right?

219
00:15:00,424 --> 00:15:02,025
You're a chatty guy!

220
00:15:02,025 --> 00:15:04,823
So in order to not get caught
by the shadow Senbons...

221
00:15:04,895 --> 00:15:06,760
I'm alert to the trick
and look closely...

222
00:15:09,099 --> 00:15:09,622
What?!

223
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:11,094
Behind?!

224
00:15:16,373 --> 00:15:16,964
<i>String?</i>

225
00:15:18,575 --> 00:15:19,405
Damn it!

226
00:15:19,476 --> 00:15:20,135
Too late!

227
00:15:22,245 --> 00:15:23,234
Shikamaru!

228
00:15:23,347 --> 00:15:24,905
He took that pretty bad.

229
00:15:25,315 --> 00:15:27,613
It wasn't that bad, look closely.

230
00:15:27,684 --> 00:15:28,150
Huh?

231
00:15:28,452 --> 00:15:31,285
F-For the moment I dodged a fatal hit.

232
00:15:32,756 --> 00:15:34,314
Now it's my turn!

233
00:15:34,591 --> 00:15:36,024
That's not going to happen.

234
00:15:46,169 --> 00:15:48,160
W-What's this?

235
00:15:54,644 --> 00:15:58,944
That happens to anyone
who hears my bell.

236
00:16:00,417 --> 00:16:02,942
The sound vibration of
this special bell

237
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:06,289
reaches the brain directly
from the ear drum.

238
00:16:06,923 --> 00:16:09,756
And then it will make you hallucinate.

239
00:16:13,029 --> 00:16:13,825
It's useless!

240
00:16:14,030 --> 00:16:17,056
You can't avoid the sound of
my bell by doing...

241
00:16:17,134 --> 00:16:21,070
that... that... that... that... that...

242
00:16:21,304 --> 00:16:24,535
Shoot! Which one?
Which is the real one?

243
00:16:25,709 --> 00:16:27,574
You can't do anything, can you?

244
00:16:27,944 --> 00:16:33,746
Your shadow, which was your faint hope,
doesn't even know where to stretch to...

245
00:16:36,553 --> 00:16:39,454
Well... I'll cook you slowly.

246
00:16:41,825 --> 00:16:43,053
Taking me lightly!

247
00:16:48,965 --> 00:16:52,059
This time it's five,
next time seven...

248
00:16:52,869 --> 00:16:56,430
I'll continue until you become
a hedgehog.

249
00:16:57,007 --> 00:16:58,907
Y-You're lying, you brat!

250
00:16:59,075 --> 00:16:59,564
Huh?!

251
00:17:00,310 --> 00:17:01,834
You'd end it soon...

252
00:17:01,912 --> 00:17:03,402
That's what you said
in the beginning, isn't it?

253
00:17:04,247 --> 00:17:08,240
I see, you can't endure the pain
and want to be eased.

254
00:17:09,953 --> 00:17:12,251
Well, I'll finish it here.

255
00:17:13,857 --> 00:17:14,789
It's your death warrant.

256
00:17:20,263 --> 00:17:21,287
W-What?!

257
00:17:22,833 --> 00:17:24,027
M-My body...

258
00:17:27,270 --> 00:17:30,000
At last, Shadow Possession Jutsu
is a success.

259
00:17:31,541 --> 00:17:33,236
W-What are you saying?

260
00:17:33,543 --> 00:17:36,205
No way!
Your shadow isn't anywhere...

261
00:17:37,214 --> 00:17:38,875
You don't realize it yet?

262
00:17:39,583 --> 00:17:41,073
I-It can't be...

263
00:17:42,118 --> 00:17:43,915
It's just that, you fool!

264
00:17:45,288 --> 00:17:48,815
A thread at this height
can't have a shadow.

265
00:17:49,593 --> 00:17:53,529
I can stretch and shrink
my own shadow.

266
00:17:54,865 --> 00:17:56,696
The shadow is gradually getting thicker.

267
00:17:57,801 --> 00:18:00,099
This wasn't the shadow of the thread...

268
00:18:00,270 --> 00:18:02,864
That's right. I stretched my shadow
and made it narrow,

269
00:18:02,973 --> 00:18:06,704
so it looked like the shadow of
a thread and stuck it on you.

270
00:18:10,313 --> 00:18:13,282
But... How do you win with that?

271
00:18:13,817 --> 00:18:15,842
I'm just gonna move
the same way as you.

272
00:18:16,186 --> 00:18:17,380
Annoying.

273
00:18:17,554 --> 00:18:18,816
Be quiet and watch.

274
00:18:25,896 --> 00:18:26,692
Stupid!

275
00:18:27,531 --> 00:18:29,431
If you continue like this and attack...

276
00:18:29,599 --> 00:18:31,897
You, too,
will be wounded!

277
00:18:33,436 --> 00:18:34,869
I know that.

278
00:18:36,373 --> 00:18:37,738
No way! You're!

279
00:18:38,475 --> 00:18:40,210
We're gonna throw shuriken
at each other.

280
00:18:40,210 --> 00:18:41,404
How far will we go?

281
00:18:41,545 --> 00:18:42,375
Fool, stop it!

282
00:18:49,252 --> 00:18:50,446
<i>You're only talk...</i>

283
00:18:52,656 --> 00:18:53,850
And that one's a goner.

284
00:18:56,059 --> 00:18:57,083
If you're a shinobi,

285
00:18:57,160 --> 00:19:00,129
you have to grasp the situation
and the layout when you battle.

286
00:19:00,797 --> 00:19:02,788
Even though we made
the same movements...

287
00:19:03,366 --> 00:19:08,235
the distance of the walls behind
each of us was different.

288
00:19:09,039 --> 00:19:10,529
I just used the shuriken and

289
00:19:10,607 --> 00:19:14,737
called attention away
from the wall behind us.

290
00:19:15,512 --> 00:19:17,639
Winner! Shikamaru Nara.

291
00:19:17,881 --> 00:19:19,815
Good job Shikamaru!

292
00:19:20,150 --> 00:19:21,412
Cool!

293
00:19:21,518 --> 00:19:22,450
Me next...

294
00:19:22,519 --> 00:19:24,817
Me next... Me next!

295
00:19:25,355 --> 00:19:29,553
That guy's dull and plain,
but that was kinda cool.

296
00:19:29,726 --> 00:19:30,454
Shoot!

297
00:19:31,428 --> 00:19:33,896
<i>I'm the only one left.</i>

298
00:19:34,631 --> 00:19:36,826
And the next match.

299
00:19:37,500 --> 00:19:39,730
The people left are one Sound ninja,

300
00:19:39,936 --> 00:19:43,201
me, Hinata, Naruto, Choji, Neji and Lee.

301
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:45,073
And that Sand guy...

302
00:19:46,009 --> 00:19:48,773
Just please spare me from that guy.

303
00:19:50,313 --> 00:19:53,612
This year's rookie looks quite challenging...

304
00:20:05,929 --> 00:20:08,762
Naruto Uzumaki vs. Kiba Inuzuka

305
00:20:09,299 --> 00:20:11,494
It's here, it's here, it's here!

306
00:20:11,768 --> 00:20:13,258
What we've been waiting for!

307
00:20:13,436 --> 00:20:15,927
It's finally my turn!

308
00:20:16,072 --> 00:20:18,472
Yeah! Lucky us!

309
00:20:18,541 --> 00:20:21,339
If it's this guy
we'll absolutely win, Akamaru!

310
00:20:23,079 --> 00:20:24,444
Yahoo!

311
00:20:24,581 --> 00:20:26,845
- If I'm not next, Sakura will despise me...
- I'm gonna do it!

312
00:20:26,916 --> 00:20:29,282
- And call me Bushy Brow.
- I'm gonna go for it!

313
00:20:29,519 --> 00:20:32,511
- If I'm not next. Sakura will...
- Just watch me! Yay!

314
00:20:32,889 --> 00:20:36,518
<i>This Lee kid, he's just like</i>
<i>Guy was in the past...</i>

315
00:20:42,966 --> 00:20:44,456
Do your best, Naruto.

316
00:20:44,901 --> 00:20:46,664
Leave it to me.

317
00:20:47,637 --> 00:20:50,435
<i>Well Naruto, show us...</i>

318
00:20:51,174 --> 00:20:52,766
<i>how much you've grown.</i>

319
00:20:56,479 --> 00:20:57,912
I'm going to do it!

320
00:21:06,753 --> 00:21:11,213
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

321
00:21:11,290 --> 00:21:19,698
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

322
00:21:20,633 --> 00:21:29,371
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

323
00:21:29,742 --> 00:21:37,615
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

324
00:21:38,885 --> 00:21:44,551
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

325
00:21:44,624 --> 00:21:48,390
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

326
00:21:48,461 --> 00:21:52,022
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

327
00:21:52,365 --> 00:22:00,898
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

328
00:22:01,174 --> 00:22:06,373
<i>when you want to cry,</i>
<i>and you want to run away</i>

329
00:22:06,446 --> 00:22:10,849
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

330
00:22:10,917 --> 00:22:14,683
<i>Just sing.</i>

331
00:22:14,921 --> 00:22:20,086
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

332
00:22:20,159 --> 00:22:22,354
<i>The two are one</i>

333
00:22:22,462 --> 00:22:28,731
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

334
00:22:29,235 --> 00:22:34,332
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

335
00:22:38,473 --> 00:22:40,441
Damn that Kiba!

336
00:22:40,509 --> 00:22:43,205
I hold back a little bit and
he rides my brain.

337
00:22:43,278 --> 00:22:44,870
Yap, yap, yap, yap,
it's annoying! Believe it!

338
00:22:45,013 --> 00:22:47,811
Just quit talking tough, and use your dog
or whatever, and come at me!

339
00:22:48,049 --> 00:22:50,540
I don't know what kind of
training you've done,

340
00:22:50,619 --> 00:22:53,144
but I'm the man who's going
to become Hokage.

341
00:22:53,221 --> 00:22:56,884
You're the one who's going
to get his butt kicked.

342
00:22:57,592 --> 00:23:01,084
Next time: "Akamaru Unleashed!
Who's Top Dog Now?"

343
00:23:01,396 --> 00:23:03,364
Don't take me lightly!
